member.summary:
Recursively traverses a directory tree and invokes a callback for each file encountered.
The callback may control traversal flow (continue, skip children, or stop traversal).


Traverse("res://", entry => GD.Print(entry.FullPath));

Creates a pool of nodes to eliminate expensive QueueFree calls.

// Create the pool
ComponentPool<Projectile> pool = new(parentNode, () => projectilePackedScene.Instantiate());

// Get a projectile from the pool
Projectile projectile = pool.Acquire();

// Projectile goes off screen or dies
projectile.Release(); // Never use QueueFree()

